INSERT INTO resources (
                id,
                name,
                namespace,
                resource_type,
                manifest,
                hash
            ) VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
            ON CONFLICT (resource_type, name, namespace)
            DO UPDATE SET 
                manifest = $5,
                hash = $6,
                updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
